{"tid":897981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"丹尼爾艾維斯：被哥迪奧拿執教比做愛更爽！","createTime":"2018-11-11T11:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:53:17.000Z","uid":122,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d2c9006cde1221b3dd4d99f28cbe3afba4620a","tid":897981,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:09:28.000Z","msg":"如今身在巴黎聖日耳門的前巴塞大將艾維斯近日在接受《天空體育》採訪時表達了對哥迪奧拿的讚賞，稱：「被他執教勝過做愛」，而哥迪奧拿也回應了他的言論。<br />\n<br />\n　　艾維斯：「哥迪奧拿作為一名足球運動員教會了我很多東西，這也是為什麼每次我被問到相同的問題總會說：他是我合作過的最佳教練。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「他在關鍵時刻是個天才，他值得如何讓球員明白要做什麼，在很多情況下，他都是為我們贏得比賽的教練，我們只是按照他的指示去做。從我第一次和哥迪奧拿聊天，他就非常清楚自己想要什麼，他想做一些不一樣的事。我知道一開始這就是個挑戰，而他對我說：只有你跟著我一起，我才能做到。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「在哥迪奧拿手下踢球要好過做愛。」艾維斯表示。<br />\n　　而在哥迪奧拿聽到這番言論後在新聞記者會上幽默地回應道：「我還是更喜歡做愛。」"},{"pid":"21b50b91d30d40e14e69802035ae95e5d9a63e74","tid":897981,"uid":122,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/CWa6m1dOxk3sY/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FCWa6m1dOxk3sY%2Fsource.gif&h=7b129115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d767f07b683444012b9a65bc3fc1f4683841f2d5","tid":897981,"uid":1039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737dd697ec9ced7f1a5705b79ab65918b7a980a9","tid":897981,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:14:32.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dd4fe9a22ceac0ced108020b7f8479929ceb64","tid":897981,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/ent/4_ori/upload/cf535fca/20170707/ee5N-fyhwres7821262.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt